Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to bring to the market for lease, one of the finest commercial office offerings available in the Near City. Situated in a prime position in the middle of the Gasworks, this fully fitted out office opportunity is one not to be missed. Key features of the property include:

-  Approx. 650-1,358sqm fitted out A Grade office
-  Freestanding building opportunity with retail exposure 
-  Exclusive building foyer 
-  16 secure exclusive car parks
-  Exceptional natural light throughout 
-  Exclusive balcony overlooking the Gasometer 

Located in the Gasworks, the property has direct access to award winning cafes, restaurants, public transport and out door break out and entertainment areas. 

The Annex at 76 Skyring Terrace is an extremely rare opportunity which is suited to a variety of users including medical, office and retailers. 

For more information or to arrange an inspection, contact the exclusive agents above. 

0-Star Nabers Energy Rating

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: YOUR OWN A GRADE BUILDING IN THE GASWORKS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Providing a variety of spaces the London offices offer all tenants the opportunity to have their business located in an iconic Brisbane building.

The building has had significant investment to maintain the character and feel of the site, with art pieces tastefully presented through common areas, London Coffee shop on the ground floor and a high quality of fit outs overall.

Public transport is readily available via Council bus services and Brisbane City Cat services.

The area has a broad range of eating and entertainment options along Vernon Terrace and Florence Street, providing abundant local amenity for staff.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the CBRE agents.

Newstead is one of the most in demand areas in the City Fringe. This property is only a short walk to the Gasworks Retail, Homemaker and Emporium precincts offering staff excellent F&B and lifestyle amenity.

Current Availability: Level 1

• High quality fitout in place featuring 45 open plan workstations, 6 offices, meeting spaces, large breakout area.
• Onsite and street parking available
• Great natural light throughout 
• Showers and Bike Racks

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact Exclusive Agents CBRE and JLL.
